            <p class="hca-text--subhead hca-text__color--asphalt">Icons are an important part of any digital design when used correctly. They can communicate when words may fail to communicate, and they can give clarity to an action that a user may want or need to take.</p>
            <p class="hca-text--subhead hca-text__color--asphalt">Below are specific guidelines for how HCA Design System utilizes common user interface icons. Adhereing to these guidelines helps ensure a consistent experience for all users when they experience a digital product from HCA.</p>
